:Namespace InitializeTests

‚ćĚ Initialize jarvis resolves the absolute app config path ($APL_SERVICE_APP_CONFIG
‚ćĚ if set, else config/app.config.json next to jarvis.CodeSource), loads it
‚ćĚ with LoadAppConfig, and assigns the global AppState.RootFolder. jarvis is
‚ćĚ whatever Jarvis passes for a monadic AppInitFn: a stub namespace exposing
‚ćĚ just .CodeSource is enough here, since Initialize touches nothing else on
‚ćĚ it. The $APL_SERVICE_APP_CONFIG override itself is not exercised here: a
‚ćĚ running interpreter cannot set its own environment variables, so that
‚ćĚ path is covered by the e2e smoke test, which launches a real subprocess
‚ćĚ with the variable set.

